1. Each purchase of the FunTV weekly/monthly subscription package immediately grants a set amount of bonus. 
2. For weekly subscriptions, log in each day within 7 days to claim daily bonuses (missing a day's login means missing that day's bonus). 
3. For monthly subscriptions, log in each day within 30 days to claim daily bonuses (missing a day's login means missing that day's bonus). 
4. Within the subscription period, you can claim the daily bonus starting at 00:00 each day in your local time zone. 
5. Your Play Store account will be automatically charged for the renewal fee 24 hours before the current subscription period ends. 
6. To avoid charges, disable auto-renewal in the Play Store settings - Manage Subscriptions at least 24 hours before the current period ends. 
7. If you have any questions, please contact us through the feedback section on your profile page.
